# RealtimePlotSphere - Live Metric Visualizer

RealtimePlotSphere renders incoming data in real time using smooth, scrollable Matplotlib-based graphs.

## Features
- Scrollable chart  
- Adjustable frame rate  
- Lightweight UI  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/33_RealtimePlotSphere.git
cd 33_RealtimePlotSphere
python visualize.py
